25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：需要在 Linux 主机上排查入侵痕迹的运维和蓝队同学。\n阅读前提：了解进程、网络连接、系统日志与计划任务。\n核心收获：建立从进程、用户、网络到文件系统的排查顺序。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Linux 服务器因其在 Web 服务、数据库、容器平台等关键基础设施中的广泛应用，一直是攻击者的重点目标。相比 Windows，Linux 系统的入侵排查更依赖命令行工具和对系统底层机制的深入理解。本文将从入侵迹象识别出发，系统讲解 Linux 环境下的用户、进程、网络、定时任务、文件系统和日志六大排查维度，并介绍 Rootkit 检测方法。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"linux-入侵迹象识别","children":["Linux 入侵迹象识别",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#linux-入侵迹象识别","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在正式开展排查之前，以下异常现象通常是系统已被入侵的信号："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"系统资源异常"}],"：CPU 或内存持续高负载，且无法对应到已知业务进程"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"异常网络流量"}],"：出现大量对外连接，尤其是连接到非常规端口或境外 IP"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"陌生用户账户"}],"：",["$","code",null,{"children":"/etc/passwd"}]," 中出现未知用户，特别是 UID 为 0 的非 root 账户"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"文件被篡改"}],"：系统关键文件（如 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"/etc/crontab"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"children":"/root/.bashrc"}],"）的修改时间异常"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"日志异常"}],"：日志文件被清空、大小突然为零，或出现大量认证失败记录"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"可疑定时任务"}],"：出现未知的 crontab 条目或 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"/etc/cron.d/"}]," 下的异常文件"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"异常进程"}],"：发现名称伪装为系统进程、运行在 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"/tmp"}]," 或 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"/dev/shm"}]," 下的进程"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"用户账户排查","children":["用户账户排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#用户账户排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"用户账户是攻击者进入系统的门户，也是持久化的重要手段。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检查用户列表","children":["检查用户列表",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检查用户列表","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检查登录记录","children":["检查登录记录",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检查登录记录","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检查-sudo-和特权操作","children":["检查 sudo 和特权操作",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检查-sudo-和特权操作","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"进程排查","children":["进程排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#进程排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"进程排查是发现正在运行的恶意程序的最直接方式。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"基础进程检查","children":["基础进程检查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#基础进程检查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"深度进程分析","children":["深度进程分析",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#深度进程分析","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-lsof-排查","children":["使用 lsof 排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-lsof-排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L35","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"网络连接排查","children":["网络连接排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#网络连接排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"恶意程序几乎都需要网络通信，无论是接收 C2 指令、外传数据还是进行横向移动。"}],"\n","$L36","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"定时任务排查","children":["定时任务排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#定时任务排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"定时任务（Cron）是 Linux 系统上最常用的持久化机制之一。"}],"\n","$L37","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"自启动服务排查","children":["自启动服务排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#自启动服务排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L38","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"文件系统排查","children":["文件系统排查",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#文件系统排查","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"查找近期修改的文件","children":["查找近期修改的文件",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#查找近期修改的文件","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L39","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检查-suidsgid-文件","children":["检查 SUID/SGID 文件",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检查-suidsgid-文件","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"SUID 文件以文件所有者权限运行，攻击者常利用此机制提权。"}],"\n","$L3a","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检查可疑位置","children":["检查可疑位置",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检查可疑位置","children":"$L3b"}]]}],"\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50"]
